Conditional           -> Statement
Debug                 -> Special
Define                -> PreProc
Delimiter             -> Special
Exception             -> Statement
Float                 -> Constant
Function              -> Identifier
Include               -> PreProc
Keyword               -> Statement
Macro                 -> PreProc
Number                -> Constant
PreCondit             -> PreProc
Repeat                -> Statement
SpecialChar           -> Special
SpecialComment        -> Special
StatusLineTerm        -> StatusLine
StatusLineTermNC      -> StatusLineNC
StorageClass          -> Type
String                -> Constant
Structure             -> Type
Tag                   -> Special
Typedef               -> Type
lCursor               -> Cursor
CurSearch             -> Search
CursorLineFold        -> CursorLine
CursorLineSign        -> CursorLine
LineNrAbove           -> LineNr
LineNrBelow           -> LineNr
MessageWindow         -> Pmenu
PopupNotification     -> Todo
TabPanelFill          -> EndOfBuffer
TabPanel              -> EndOfBuffer
TabPanelSel           -> TabLineSel
; }}}

; Color palette {{{
; Color name         GUI                     Base256     Base16 (optional)

; This is messy for a good reason : isolating the colorschemes from ansi0-15,
; which simply cannot be relied upon.

